article_id:2777,category_name:News,title_name:Alberian Battle Royale Updated!,image_path:,message:<div>The following adjustments were made to the Alberian Battle Royale on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1661925600"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Shapeshifting Dragon Updated</div><div>All adventurers (regardless of weapon type) will now shapeshift into Midgardsormr. Future events may feature a different dragon.</div><div><br></div><div>Before: Reborn Nidhogg</div><div>After: Midgardsormr</div><div><br></div><div>■Monthly Battle Point Rewards Updated</div><div>Monthly battle point rewards were updated on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1661925600"></span> and will be available until <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1664517599"></span>. Players can obtain various rewards based on the amount of battle points they earn each month.</div><div><br></div><div>■Treasure Trade Lineup Updated</div><div>The monthly lineup in the Alberian Battle Royale Treasure Trade was updated on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1661925600"></span> and will be available until <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1664517599"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1661925600,update_time1642132517